headline: IDF detains 6 Islamic Jihad terrorists in Hebron
description: IDF forces operating in the Hebron area detained six Islamic Jihad terrorists early Saturday. The six were taken in for questioning. (Ynetnews)
articleBody: IDF forces operating in the Hebron area detained six Islamic Jihad terrorists early Saturday. The six were taken in for questioning. (Ynetnews)
